"Well,  looks like they got alot of buggers down here.  I ganer if 
they have a pub,"  He commented as his snake head on the end of his 
tail glanced around.
"Quickstrike terrorize!"  He converted back to his robot form.
"So you guys got a sign up form for kickin' butt?"  He asked the 
four guards.
